<br>
I figure everyones asking for comments, so please offer any you may have.. I'm looking for suggestions or opinions on where I'm at compared to others when it comes to gear and weapons. I feel very lacking around warrior guildies. Cash is never on hand. I have 60pp to this chars name; maybe 5k on all my chars combined.<br>
I'm an AC and DEX whore. Sad part is that AC is low for what I'm wanting. I hold up well in fights. Agro is pretty well with dex buffed up and both weaps proccing but I want more dps. Getting rid of my 2hser soon for either armor money or another decent 2hander for cheap.<br>
<br>
Anways, rip me apart please while I stroll through the forums. Any opinions welcomed.<br>
<br>
