<br>
Since you are low on funds I will suggest the following ( and please give up on valueing dex before AC/HP/STA if you do now ).  I am guessing that you will come out with a little money after this.<br>
<br>
Sell the following:<br>
<br>
Gantru Charm<br>
SCHW (they are useless to you with Myrm gloves)<br>
Cloak of Shadows<br>
Your current Visor<br>
Sonic Earring<br>
Chitenous Belt<br>
Your 10AC ring<br>
One of your bracers<br>
<br>
Buy the following:<br>
<br>
Bracer of Defense<br>
FBSS<br>
Crystal Spider eyes<br>
Spider Fur Cloak (cloak of Maelstrom if possible)<br>
Velium Fire Wedding ring<br>
Vah Shir Claw Earring<br>
<br>
This is just my opinion and you might want to get a feel for the prices of these items to see if your sell list will pay for your buy list.  I would also look at what your AC and HP's do in your magelo before starting.<br>
<br>
You state your aggro is fine now but you want more DPS.  You should have two &quot;decent&quot; DPS weapons if they proc with any consistency.  Warriors need aggro and then AC/HP's second to absorb the damage from gaining aggro.  We are not a damage class <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
If you want to go for damage then I would suggest a Frostbringer as it should up your DPS while maintaining/increasing aggro.  Otherwise you will have to go for a good two hander like a windblade IMO and those are quite pricey on Tunare anyway.<br>
<br>
Friedrick - 63rd Warlord on Tunare server<br>
